        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "His weapon.—Or, his missiles, arms. LXX., ὅπλοα. (Comp. 2Chronicles 32:5.) Kings has a commoner word. The remainder of the verse is identical with its parallel.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "His weapon.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—Or, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "his missiles, arms.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " LXX., ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "greekheb",
            "text": "ὅπλοα.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " (Comp. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "2Chronicles 32:5",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ".) Kings has a commoner word. The remainder of the verse is identical with its parallel.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Along by.—Towards the altar.",
        "children": [
